Reasoning: The paper discusses adding auxiliary variables to TLA+ specifications for the purpose of verifying correctness, which suggests a focus on logic and formal methods (cs.LO). The use of auxiliary variables is also relevant to programming languages and compilers (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper's application to a snapshot algorithm suggests a focus on distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS).
